title: Boston Chamber's Singh on Boston's Thriving Tech Scene (Audio)
itunes:title: Boston Chamber's Singh on Boston's Thriving Tech Scene (Audio)
description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Nav Singh, Managing Partner at the McKinsey Boston office and Chair of the Boston Chamber of Commerce, on this year's annual event and the evolution of the Boston tech and biotech scene. Broadcasting live from the Boston Convention and Exhibition Center.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
